name: 3D-Platformer (infa-education)
description:
3D-Platformer from Anani Bareyan with Assets from MSU.

Changes compared to the training version:

1. Original Level 1 and Level 2

2. New in-game menu

3. New environments and enemies (from 3D-Shotter)

4. New futuristic objects, wall and floor materials, transparent windows

5. New kind of obstacle (JumpPad+Hallway)
